75
00:08:08,178 --> 00:08:12,456
Nisam. Morao sam da
uzmem neke papire i sitnice.

76
00:08:14,058 --> 00:08:16,731
Zar ti nije dosadno?

77
00:08:16,898 --> 00:08:18,570
Ne.

78
00:08:18,738 --> 00:08:20,968
Pa, ostavljam te
u toj vrućini.

79
00:08:21,138 --> 00:08:23,131
Dođi i zagrli me.

80
00:08:43,778 --> 00:08:47,612
Ne, bićeš skroz mokar.
Izvini.

81
00:08:50,698 --> 00:08:52,973
Nema veze.

82
